===Wikipedia Drama===
Since furry existence revolves around [[WikiEdit Drama]], many of [[Wikipedia]]'s admins are furfags, such as: [[ContiE]], Fennec, Furrykef, KieferSkunk, Loganberry, Wiki alf, and [[User:Wwwwolf|Wwwwolf]] - all of whom are the same person. There is also Krishva, who insists her childhood was destroyed forevar by furries and has made it her lifelong goal in life to make sure that web sites such as [[Wikipedia]], are as accurate (read: white-washed) as possible. This involved making approximately eleventy gazillion edits to [[Wikipedia:Furry|Wikipedia's "Furry" article]] and, when that didn't fulfill her need for alpha-wolf dominance, also the [[Wikipedia:Furry_fandom|"Furry fandom"]], [[Wikipedia:Funny_animal|"Funny animal"]], and [[Wikipedia:Talking_animal|"Talking animal"]] articles.

Why in the world Wikipedia has separate articles for "Furry" and "Furry Fandom" in the first place is one of the many [[Shit nobody cares about|infinitesimally trivial points]] being bickered about by Krishva in the various articles' [[talk page]]s. Why? Because certain furfags want to [[lie|deny that furry has anything to do with sex]]. There is one [[yiff]] pic in existence that doesn't resemble [[:Image:Dancers.jpg|this]] and they put it on their yiff article. Obsessively denying the relation between sex and furfags on Wikipedia is likely the result of furry-style [[castration]].

